2. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also likely as feature detection is an important aspect of image retrieval systems. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible sub-category as the paper deals with image processing and analysis. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible sub-category as some feature detectors may use machine learning techniques. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible sub-category as feature detection is an important aspect of computer vision and AI systems.
